<span class="gu">## Post excerpts</span>
First, let's see how this and the above paragraph looks like in markdown:
<span class="nt">&lt;</span><span class="err">!â€“</span><span class="na">-break-</span><span class="err">â€“</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
